 </m:mrow>

</m:math></para>
    <para id="id11540443">The only property of the impulses that have any consequences are their areas and these are the sample values. Hence, impulse modulation is an effective model of sampling; the sample values, and only the sample values, are preserved by impulse modulation.</para>
